    "Prompt Setting.",
    "We adopt the zero-shot chainof-thought prompting (Kojima et al., 2022) (dubbed Zero-Shot-CoT) to induce LLMs to generate the reasoning steps before producing the final answer.",
    "This kind of analyze-then-output process has been shown to improve reasoning performance, as well as interpretability (Zhang et al., 2023b).",
    "Task instructions are simple and clear for generality, as presented in Figure 4 Metrics.",
    "Following binary classification such as information retrieval, safety judgment uses F1 score as the ranking score of the leaderboard."
